"NSSpeechRecognitionUsageDescription" = "Provii Wallet wuxuu isticmaashaa aqoonsiga hadalka amarro codeed ahaan ee qaabka helitaanka, taas oo kuu ogolaanaysa inaad app-ka si gacanta ka xor ah u xukunto.";

/* Microphone Access */
